Package com.hhstechgroup.tests.regressionBaseline.v_PharmacyEnrollment

This Package contains test classes covering all the test stories for Pharmacy Enrollments.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    PharmacyEnrollmentVerifyDocumentReviewTest
    This class contains a test that does the document review of a pharmacy enrollment using a data provider.
    PharmacyProviderAppealAndCoCDenialProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a Coc denied of a pharmacy provider and appeals and deny it.
    PharmacyProviderAppealApprovalProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a denied pharmacy and appeals and approves it.
    PharmacyProviderAppealDenialProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a denied pharmacy, appeals and deny it.
    PharmacyProviderApproveEnrollmentTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider, approves pharmacy enrollment
    PharmacyProviderCocDenyProcessTest
    This method contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved pharmacy enrollment, creates and denies an identifying information CoC
    PharmacyProviderCocProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved pharmacy enrollment and creates and approves a change address CoC.
    PharmacyProviderCreateAndApproveSiteVisitTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved pharmacy enrollment, creates and approves site visit.
    PharmacyProviderDenyEnrollmentTest
    This test class changes the status of a Pharmacy enrollment from 'Pending Review' to 'Denied'.
    PharmacyProviderPaymentFeeVerificationTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to register a new Provider and, creates and submits an pharmacy enrollment
    PharmacyProviderPreConditionSetup
    This test class sets the Systems Option configuration for Pharmacy Provider.
    PharmacyProviderReenrollmentProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved pharmacy, terminates, re-enrolls and approves the enrollment
    PharmacyProviderRegistrationAndSubmissionTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to register a new Provider, Creates and submits a pharmacy enrollment
    PharmacyProviderRequestForAdditionalInfoDenyTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get a pharmacy enrollment with "Pending review" status , requests for additional information and denies the enrollment
    PharmacyProviderSubmitScreeningTest
    This class contains a test that under screens a pharmacy enrollment using a data provider.
    PharmacyProviderTerminateSuspendReactiveProcessTest
    This class contains a test which uses a data provider to get an approved pharmacy,suspends, terminates and reactive.
